        <DOC>
            	<DOCNO>s_1766_467_1</DOCNO>
            	<TEXT>The single most common suggestion I see regarding how to nerf Shatterdive is to nerf Glaciers so that the divers can keep the dive.</TEXT>
        </DOC>
        <DOC>
            	<DOCNO>s_1766_467_2</DOCNO>
