            	<TEXT>1) Removing the freeze on crystal formation will hurt the howl aspect and the super and further make the slam pointless.</TEXT>
        </DOC>
        <DOC>
            	<DOCNO>s_1766_470_2</DOCNO>
            	<TEXT>2) Reducing the crystal shatter damage will nerf shatterdive but will also nerf cryo just as much (and it's already worse than the dive).</TEXT>
