        <DOC>
            	<DOCNO>s_1766_470_4</DOCNO>
            	<TEXT>3) Reducing the number of Crystals spawned will only nerf the tectonic aspect to give less shards (as it stands, tectonic is the weakest of the harvest aspects in pve).</TEXT>
        </DOC>
        <DOC>
            	<DOCNO>s_1766_470_5</DOCNO>
            	<TEXT>Unless they tune Hunter (whether it's the dive or ToW) individually, any global nerf just serves as a net bigger nerf to Behemoth (already a low/mid tier class relatively).</TEXT>
