            	<DOCNO>s_1766_471_2</DOCNO>
            	<TEXT>Fissures adds an additional tick of 22 damage per explosion (that has it's own range) making the max possible damage 385 but again, that won't happen since even if you are standing by the centre crystal, the falloff of the outer crystals comes into effect (so it can't kill supers).</TEXT>
